quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Nnipa nkontabuo (berε no) abεn wͻn, nanso wͻ’de anibianaso twi fa so"
  21,2,"Afutusεm foforͻ biara a ebefri wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ aba wͻn hͻ no, gyesε wͻ’tie no agodie mu (anaasε wͻ’fa no fεwdie)"
  21,3,"Nsεm hunu na ԑwᴐ wͻn akoma mu. Abͻneεfoͻ no tu agyina kokoa mu (ka sε): “Woi nyε nipa sε moara? Mode moho bεma ntafowa anaa naadaasεm aberε a moani tua?”"
  21,4,"(Nkͻmhyεni) kaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn Nim asεm biara a εwͻ soro ne asaase so, na Ɔne Otiefoͻ no a Ɔte biribiara, na Ɔno ara ne Onimdefoͻ no a Onim biribiara no"
  21,5,"Daabi, wͻ’ka sε: (Saa Adiyisεm yi tesε) daeε so bi a adi afra. Daabi, w’abͻ netrim (na atwerε), Daabi, ͻyε dwom-toni! (Sε εnte saa a) εneε ͻnfa nsεnkyerεnee bi sεdeε yεde somaa tetefoͻ no (asomafoͻ no) bi mmrε yεn“"
  21,6,Nkuro a Ye’dii wͻn anim kan sεee wͻn no mu biara nnihͻ a wͻ’gye diiε. Enti wͻn bεgye adi anaa
  21,7,"(Wᴐn a) Y’edii w’anim kan somaa wᴐn no na wᴐ‎’yԑ nnipa na Ye’yii Adiyisεm no maa wͻn. Enti (Makafoͻ a moregye Muhammad akyinnyeε) sε monnim a, momisa wͻn a wͻ’kaekae (amanfoͻ) no"
  21,8,"Na Y’amma Asomafoͻ no honam a enni aduane, na Y’annyε wͻn (nnipa a) wͻ’bεtena (wiase) afe bͻͻ (na wͻn nwuo)"
  21,9,"Enti Yedii bͻhyε no ho nokorε maa wͻn, na Y’εgyee wͻn ne wͻn a Y’εpε no nkwa, na Y’εsεee nsεmͻnedifoͻ no"
  21,10,"(Adasamma), ampa sε Y’asiane Nwoma a moho afutusεm, moanimuonyam ne monkͻsoͻ ho asεm wͻ mu. Enti monnte (saa adom kεseε yi) ase"
  21,11,Nkuro dodoɔ sɛn na na wͻ’yε abͻneεfoͻ a Yε’sεee no? Ɛno akyiri no Yε’bͻͻ nnipa foforͻ (dehyεε wͻn anan mu)
  21,12,"Ɛberε a wͻ’hunuu Y’asotwee no, hwε! (Wͻ’bͻͻ mmͻden sε) wͻ’redwane no"
  21,13,"Monhwε na moandwane, na mmom monsan nkͻ moahodwoͻ abrabͻ a mowͻ mu no mu, ne moasetena a mowͻ mu no mu sεdeε yεbebisa mo asεm"
  21,14,"Wͻ’kaa sε: Adi ayε yεn! Nokorε sε na yε’yε abͻneεfoͻ"
  21,15,Wͻn suu no deε anyae kͻpem sε Yε’yεε wͻn sε afuo a yatwa emu nnͻbae na atεm dinn
  21,16,Ɛnyε agorͻ nti na Yεbͻͻ soro ne asaase ne deε εwͻ mfinfii no
  21,17,"Sε Yε’pε anigyesεm (sε εyerε anaa mma) a, anka Yε’bεfa no wͻ Yεn hͻ, sε Yε’pε sε yεyε (saa a)"
  21,18,"Daabi, Yε’to Nokorε no bͻ nkontompo no, na (nkontompo no) atu ayera afri hͻ korakora; na hwε na nkontompo asopa. Adi nyε mo wͻ (nkontomposεm a) mode susu (Nyankopͻn) no"
  21,19,"Nea ԑwͻ soro ne asaase soͻ (nyinaa) yε Nedea. Wͻn a wͻn wͻ Nehͻ (Soro abͻfoͻ) no nnyε Nesom ho ahomasoᴐ, na εnha wͻn anaasε wͻ’mmrε nso (wͻ Nesom ho)"
  21,20,Wͻ’bͻ (no) abodin kamfo no anadwo ne adekyeε (mu nyinaa) na wͻ’mmrε
  21,21,Anaasε wͻn anya anyame bi wͻ asaase no so a wͻ’yane awufoͻ
  21,22,"Sε anyame bi wͻ soro ne asaase so ka Nyankopͻn ho a anka (ͻsoro ne asaase) mmienu (nyinaa) asεe. Kronkron Hene ne Nyankopͻn, Animuonyam ahennie Wura no, Ɔso kyεn sεdeε wͻ’de susu no no"
  21,23,"Obiara ntumi mmisa no wͻ deε Ɔyε ho asεm, na wͻn deε yεbebisa wͻn"
  21,24,"Anaasε wͻn afri N’akyi anya anyame foforͻ bi? (Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: “Monfa mo nyinasoͻ mmra. Woi ne afutusεm dema wͻn a wͻ’ka me ho ne wͻn a wͻ’dii m’anim kan no. Daabi, wͻn mu pii nnnim Nokorε no, enti wͻ’dane wͻn ho fri ho"
  21,25,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ͻsomafoͻ biara a Ye’dii w’anim kan somaa no no, Adiyisεm a Ye’yi maa no ara ne sε, (ͻmͻ amanfoͻ no kͻkͻ) sε: “Awurade foforͻ biara nni hͻ gyesε Me nko ara enti monsom Me “"
  21,26,"Wͻ’keka sε: “Ahummͻborͻ Hene no awo ba. Kronkron Hene ne no. Daabi, wͻn (a wͻ’ka sε wͻ’yε Nyankopͻn mma tesε soro abͻfoͻ ne Yesu no nyinaa) yε (Nyankopͻn) nkoa animuonyamfoͻ"
  21,27,"Wͻ’nni Nyankopͻn anim kan nnkasa, na mmom N’ahyεdeε so na (wͻ’gyina) yε wͻn adwuma"
  21,28,"Onim deε εda wͻn anim ne deε εda wͻn akyi na wͻ’nntumi ntwitwa nnye (obi) gye nea W’agye no ato mu, na Neho suro ma wͻn ho popo"